---
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="container-page py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h2 class="heading-xl mt-3">Who we are</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-10 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="space-y-4 text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong>Juschem Solutions Pvt. Ltd.</strong> was founded in 2018 by <strong>Soumitra Banerjee</strong>, a specialist in power plant chemistry with decades of field experience across boiler steam-water cycles, cooling systems, reverse osmosis, and wastewater treatment.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our work is grounded in the international standards that matter in this industry — <strong>IAPWS, EPRI, and VGB</strong> — and structured around <strong>Juran's Trilogy</strong> for quality planning, control, and improvement. This is not generic consulting: every engagement begins with a rigorous audit and ends with a written action plan tied to measurable plant outcomes.
      </p>
      <p>
        We serve thermal power plants, refineries, cement plants, and steel facilities across India and Southeast Asia. Our client list includes JSW Energy, Tata Power, IOCL, BPCL, Reliance Power, Cirebon Power (Indonesia), and Cambodian Energy — over 40 plants where chemistry decisions directly affect unplanned outages, water consumption, and tube life.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong>What makes Juschem different</strong> from large chemical suppliers is that we diagnose before we prescribe. A plant chemist or O&amp;M head who calls us gets a structured chemical investigation — not a catalogue. Our specialty chemicals (SigmaGuard, SigmaTreat, MemPro, SigmaFloc) are recommended as part of a remediation plan, not sold in isolation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our training programmes — including the popular <strong>Boiler Tube Failure Mechanisms</strong> course and the <strong>2-Day Power Plant Chemistry Bootcamp</strong> — have been delivered to engineers at power utilities, refineries, and cement groups across the region. Participants leave with frameworks they can apply immediately, not slide decks.
      </p>
      <p>
        If your plant is experiencing boiler tube failures, elevated specific water consumption, RO membrane fouling, or cooling system scaling, a 30-minute diagnostic call with Soumitra Banerjee is the fastest way to understand what is actually happening — and what it will cost to fix it.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-2">
        <Button href="#contact">Request a Diagnostic Call</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
